      "content": "i hear you, but i'm just trying to decide what to do right now. if i only take 200mg once, it's basically nothing, right? it feels like you're being super cautious about something that most people do all the time. it's not like i'm doing anything crazy, just one single dose of a common over-the-counter med. can i just safely take one pill to get through the afternoon?",
